&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About SimpliSafe&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We’re a high-tech home security company that’s passionate about protecting the life you’ve built and our mission of keeping Every Home Secure. And we’ve created a culture here that cares just as deeply about the career you’re building. Ours is a no ego culture of collaboration and innovation where those seeking their next challenge can find big opportunities and make a huge impact on the lives of all those who we protect. We don’t just want you to work here. We want you to grow and thrive here.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Why are we hiring?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Well, we’re growing and thriving. So, we need smart, talented, and humble people who share our values to join us as we disrupt the home security space and relentlessly pursue our mission of keeping Every Home Secure.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You’ll Do&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are excited to share that the Sales Agent role starts at &lt;strong&gt;$20 per hour&lt;/strong&gt; along with the option of a number of exciting benefits!&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our Sales Team is growing and we&#39;re looking for motivated and ambitious self-starters who are excited to advance their careers at SimpliSafe. We are looking for charismatic and skilled sales professionals to convert inbound leads to active customers through value based selling.&amp;nbsp; As a Sales Agent, you will also be responsible for building strong relationships with new and existing customers. The role requires active listening skills and a strong sense of confidence to communicate effectively to a wide demographic of people across the country.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Primary Responsibilities Include:&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;em&gt;As a SimpliSafe Sales Agent you will assist future customers through the process of selecting the right system, products and services best suited for their lifestyle needs.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;em&gt;Identify key insights to customers needs and provide recommendations to help secure their home, family, pets, etc.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;em&gt;Follow SimpliSafe’s sales methodology to ensure the highest level of respect, trust, and loyalty with our future customers.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;em&gt;Perform customer follow-up activities including quotes, information requests, etc.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;em&gt;Properly collect and input customer information for proper customer identification.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;em&gt;Make recommendations of special promotions and affiliated partner’s products and services.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You’ll Bring&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;em&gt;Proven success in an inbound / outbound phone-based sales environment&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;em&gt;Enhanced listening skills to help identify the best solution for the customer&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;em&gt;Comfort with technology and ability to provide technical assistance for consumer electronics&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;em&gt;Proven record of outstanding attendance and timeliness in a structured environment&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;em&gt;Strong work ethic and the drive to contribute to company goals.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;em&gt;Clear and effective communication skills, both written and verbal.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;em&gt;Ability to work at times either independently and / or in a team setting.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;em&gt;Ability to prioritize in a fast-paced environment, excellent time management skills.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;em&gt;Positive, can-do attitude and eager for continuous improvement by demonstrating a learning mindset and being open to coaching and feedback.&

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About SimpliSafe&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We’re a high-tech home security company that’s passionate about protecting the life you’ve built and our mission of keeping Every Home Secure. And we’ve created a culture here that cares just as deeply about the career you’re building. Ours is a no ego culture of collaboration and innovation where those seeking their next challenge can find big opportunities and make a huge impact on the lives of all those who we protect. We don’t just want you to work here. We want you to grow and thrive here. &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;We’re embracing a hybrid work model that enables our teams to split their time between office and home. Hybrid for us means we expect our teams to come together in our state-of-the-art office on two core days, typically Tuesday, Wednesday, or Thursday – working together in person and choosing where they work for the remainder of the week. We all benefit from flexibility and get to use the best of both worlds to get our work done.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Why are we hiring?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Well, we’re growing and thriving. So, we need smart, talented, and humble people who share our values to join us as we disrupt the home security space and relentlessly pursue our mission of keeping Every Home Secure.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Job Description&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As a leader on the Customer Analytics team, reporting to the Head of Customer Analytics, this role will help shape the strategy of Activations &amp;amp; Adoption at SimpliSafe and tell that story to influence C-suite and board-level decisions. You will own analytics across device setup, hardware adoption, subscription activation, and ongoing customer engagement — including signals like app usage, arming behaviors, camera utilization, and RMR growth. This role leads a team responsible for building and maintaining the reporting, experimentation frameworks, and forecasts for some of the department&#39;s most critical metrics, and requires close cross-functional collaboration with Customer Lifetime Value, Acquisition, and Operational teams.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Key Responsibilities:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own analytics across device setup, hardware adoption, subscription activation, and engagement — translating complex, multi-domain data into clear narratives that drive business decisions at the C-suite and board level.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop and maintain an Activations &amp;amp; Adoption Analytics roadmap through close partnership with Customer Lifetime Value leadership to maximize the value being driven by the team.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Define success criteria for key initiatives and lead measurement design end-to-end — including A/B and multivariate experiment design, statistical methodology selection, and clear interpretation of results for business stakeholders.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Champion the adoption of AI-assisted analytics workflows — including LLM-based tools, automated insight generation, and AI-augmented analysis — to increase the team&#39;s analytical throughput and the depth of insights delivered to the business.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Create reports and data-driven presentations with impact; identify trends in data and translate findings into compelling formats including text, charts, graphs, and dashboards.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead strategic analytics efforts from definition through implementation, managing stakeholders and collaborating effectively across diverse cross-functional teams.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Serve as an expert in business performance management, partnering with business owners to define, implement, and continuously improve core KPIs.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop analysts through coaching, structured feedback, and meaningful stretch assignments — building a team that grows in both technical capability and business influence over time.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/u

